					"title": "Monthly Billiard News Round-Up May",
					"excerpt": "Billiards on the Rise: Key Developments Shaping the Future of Cue Sports!",
					"content": [
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h1", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Billiards on the Rise: Key Developments Shaping the Future of Cue Sports!" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "The world of billiards is buzzing with exciting news! From major international multi-sport inclusion to groundbreaking efforts in youth development and high-level recognition, cue sports are firmly on an upward trajectory." }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Pool Takes Center Stage at The World Games 2029!" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "In a monumental announcement for the sport, billiards has been officially included in The World Games 2029 program! This prestigious multi-sport event, often seen as a stepping stone to the Olympic Games, offers an incredible platform for pool to shine on a global stage." }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "WPA Champions Inclusivity with Junior & Parasport Heyball World Championships 2026" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "The World Pool-Billiard Association (WPA) continues its forward-thinking approach with the exciting announcement of the WPA Junior & Parasport Heyball World Championships 2026, set to take place in Oslo, Norway." }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "h2", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "WPBSA Drives Snooker's Influence and Inclusivity Forward" }] },
						{ "_type": "block", "style": "normal", "children": [{ "_type": "span", "text": "Meanwhile, the World Professional Billiards and Snooker Association (WPBSA) has been proactive in advancing snooker's standing. A notable success was the recent World Women's Snooker Day held at the Halo World Championship." }] }
					]
				},
				"taxonomies": { "category": ["monthly-roundup"], "tag": ["wpa", "wpbsa"] }
			},
